938.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?mon WHERE {  ?type rdfs:subClassOf+ yago:wordnet_church_103028079. ?mon a ?type . ?mon yago:isLocatedIn yago:New_York_City.  }

200.Question: Is Plymouth near Cardiff?
200.Query: ASK { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Plymouth>  geo:hasGeometry ?o. ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT. <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Cardiff> geo:hasGeometry ?o1.  ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. FILTER(geof:distance(?geoWKT,?geoWKT1, uom:metre) <= 5000) }

261.Question: Is Belfast west of London?
261.Query: ASK {    <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/resource/geoentity_City_of_Belfast_3333223> geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo.     ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT.      <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/geoentity_City_of_London_2643744> geo:hasGeometry ?ygeo.     ?ygeo geo:asWKT ?yWKT.   FILTER (strdf:left(?xWKT, ?yWKT)) }

176.Question: Is Sfakia in Scotland?
176.Query: ASK {   <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Sfakia> geo:hasGeometry ?o.   ?o geo:asWKT ?pWKT.   <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Scotland> geo:hasGeometry ?o1.   ?o1 geo:asWKT ?sWKT.   FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?pWKT, ?sWKT)) }

910.Question: Give me the latitude and longitude of NYC.
910.Query: SELECT ?lat ?lon  WHERE {      yago:New_York_City yago:hasLatitude ?lat.      yago:New_York_City yago:hasLongitude ?lon.  }

829.Question: Which 2 counties are the smallest by area?
829.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county ((strdf:area(?cWKT)) as ?totalArea) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council  }. ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT } ORDER BY (?totalArea) LIMIT 2

815.Question: Which county has the lowest population in Kansas?
815.Query: SELECT ?county  WHERE{ yago:Kansas geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?county y2geoo:hasGADM_Description "County" . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geom2 . ?geom2 geo:asWKT ?cWKT . FILTER (geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?cWKT)) . ?county y2geoo:POPULATION ?pop. }  ORDER BY ASC(xsd:double(?pop))  LIMIT 1

597.Question: Which municipalities in Greece have a population of less than 30000?
597.Query: select distinct ?x  where{ ?x a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality .  ?x geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo.  ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT.  ?x y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop.  <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Greece> geo:hasGeometry ?grgeo. ?grgeo geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?geoWKT1))  FILTER(?pop < 30000)   }

989.Question: Which is the most populated city in Missouri?
989.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?city ?pop WHERE{ ?type rdfs:subClassOf+ yago:wordnet_city_108524735 . ?city a ?type . ?city yago:isLocatedIn+ yago:Missouri . ?city yago:hasPopulation ?pop . } ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer(?pop)) LIMIT 1

153.Question: Is Oxfordshire more than 100km away from Kent?
153.Query: ASK{ yago:Oxfordshire geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?oxfWKT . yago:Kent geo:hasGeometry ?geo2 . ?geo2 geo:asWKT ?kentWKT . FILTER (geof:distance(?oxfWKT,?kentWKT,uom:metre)>100000) . }

991.Question: What is the most populated city in the State of Missouri?
991.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?city ?pop WHERE{ ?type rdfs:subClassOf+ yago:wordnet_administrative_district_108491826 . ?city a ?type . ?city yago:isLocatedIn+ yago:Missouri . ?city yago:hasPopulation ?pop . } ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer(?pop)) LIMIT 1

762.Question: Find the 3 least populated municipalities of Greece.
762.Query: SELECT distinct ?island WHERE {     ?island a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality.     ?island y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop.     ?island geo:hasGeometry ?g1.     ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1.     yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?g2.     ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2.     FILTER(         geof:sfWithin(?wkt1,?wkt2    )) } ORDER BY (?pop) LIMIT 3

92.Question: Where is Drogheda located?
92.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?geoWKT WHERE { yago:Drogheda geo:hasGeometry ?o .  ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . }

877.Question: Which island of Greece has the most beaches?
877.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?island WHERE {  yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 .  ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 .  FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && strdf:within(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1)) } GROUP BY ?island  ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?beach)) LIMIT 1

698.Question: How many streams are there in Alabama?
698.Query: SELECT (COUNT(?lake) AS ?canals)  WHERE{ yago:Alabama geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_stream . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?geol . ?geol geo:asWKT ?lWKT . FILTER (geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?lWKT)) }

204.Question: Is Howth far from Dublin?
204.Query: ASK { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Howth>  geo:hasGeometry ?g1. ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1. yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?g2. ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2. FILTER(geof:distance(?wkt1, ?wkt2, uom:metre) > 5000). }

512.Question: Which nature reserves in Ireland have lakes within their boundaries?
512.Query: SELECT  DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE {   ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve;   geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo.   ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT.   ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake;   geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo.   ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT.   <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland> geo:hasGeometry ?o1.   ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT.   FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?iWKT) && geof:sfContains(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT)) }

268.Question: Does Leicester lie to the east of Birmingham?
268.Query: ASK { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Birmingham> geo:hasGeometry ?o.     ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT.     <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Leicester> geo:hasGeometry ?o1.     ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1.     FILTER(strdf:left(?geoWKT,?geoWKT1)) }

572.Question: What are the parks situated in the forests of the United States?
572.Query: SELECT  DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE {   ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park;   geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo.   ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT.   ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest;   geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo.   ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT.    yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?o1.   ?o1 geo:asWKT ?gWKT.   FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?p2WKT, ?gWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT)) }

508.Question: Which districts of Cambridge have forests?
508.Query: SELECT distinct ?county WHERE { ?county a y2geoo:OS_District . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?countyGeo . ?countyGeo geo:asWKT ?countyWKT . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeo . ?lakeGeo geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . yago:Cambridge geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?countyWKT, ?x2WKT)) . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT,?countyWKT)) }

126.Question: Where is Luton located?
126.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?geoWKT WHERE {  yago:Luton geo:hasGeometry ?o .  ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . }

875.Question: Which district of the United Kingdom has the most villages?
875.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village . ?village geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District . ?district geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2)) } GROUP BY ?district  ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?village)) LIMIT 1

1015.Question: What is the total population of the 5 biggest cities of the United Kingdom ?
1015.Query: SELECT (SUM(xsd:integer(?pop)) as ?totalpop) WHERE { { SELECT ?city (strdf:area(?lWKT) as ?area) WHERE { yago:United_Kingdom geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_city . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?geol . ?geol geo:asWKT ?lWKT . FILTER (geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?lWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer(?area)) LIMIT 5 } ?city yago:hasPopulation ?pop.  }

850.Question: Which city in England is adjacent to the most lakes?
850.Query: SELECT ?city WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city . ?city geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?cWKT,?eWKT) && strdf:touches(?cWKT,?lWKT)) } GROUP BY (?city) ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?lake)) LIMIT 1

201.Question: Is Dublin south of Belfast?
201.Query: ASK { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Dublin> geo:hasGeometry ?o. ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT. <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/geoentity_City_of_Belfast_3333223> geo:hasGeometry ?o1.  ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. FILTER(strdf:below(?geoWKT,?geoWKT1)) }

770.Question: Which is the largest park by area in Dublin?
770.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?park ((strdf:area(?pWKT)) AS ?totalArea) WHERE {         ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park.         ?park   <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#hasGeometry> ?pGeom.         ?pGeom geo:asWKT ?pWKT.         <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Dublin> <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#hasGeometry> ?lcGeom.         ?lcGeom geo:asWKT ?lcWKT.         FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?pWKT, ?lcWKT))     } ORDER BY DESC(?totalArea) LIMIT 1

356.Question: Which districts border with the Stafford district?
356.Query: select DISTINCT ?district where { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/geoentity_Stafford_District_7290631> <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#hasGeometry> ?geomLC. ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcWKT. ?district rdf:type <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OS_District>; <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#hasGeometry> ?geomC. ?geomC geo:asWKT ?cWKT. FILTER(geof:sfTouches(?lcWKT, ?cWKT)) }

354.Question: Which are the lakes inside Central Macedonia?
354.Query: select DISTINCT ?lake WHERE{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Central_Macedonia> geo:hasGeometry ?o. ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT. ?lake <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSM_lake>. ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?o1.  ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1.  FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1,?geoWKT)) }

867.Question: Which is the smallest municipality of Greece?
867.Query: SELECT ?muni (strdf:area(?wkt) as ?area) WHERE {?muni a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality . ?muni geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?wkt . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1. ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?wkt, ?geoWKT1)) } ORDER BY DESC(?area) LIMIT 1

804.Question: Which of the municipalities that border Thessaloniki has the biggest area?
804.Query: SELECT ?neighboring (strdf:area(?yWKT)as ?totalArea) WHERE {   yago:geoentity_Dimos_Thessaloniki_8133841 geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom .   ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT .    ?neighboring a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality .   ?neighboring geo:hasGeometry ?yGeom .   ?yGeom geo:asWKT ?yWKT .       FILTER(geof:sfTouches(strdf:buffer(?xWKT,0,uom:metre), strdf:buffer(?yWKT ,0,uom:metre))) } ORDER BY DESC(?totalArea) LIMIT 1

538.Question: Which municipalities in Greece have a lake inside their boundaries?
538.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?dhmoi WHERE{ <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Greece> geo:hasGeometry ?o.  ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT.  ?lake <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>  <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSM_lake>.   ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?o1.  ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. ?dhmoi <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>  <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/GAG_Municipality>.   ?dhmoi geo:hasGeometry ?o2.  ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2.  FILTER(geof:sfWithin(strdf:transform(?geoWKT1, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>),strdf:transform(?geoWKT, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>)) && geof:sfWithin(strdf:transform(?geoWKT2, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>),strdf:transform(?geoWKT, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>)) && geof:sfWithin(strdf:transform(?geoWKT1, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>),strdf:transform(?geoWKT2, <http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326>))).  }

489.Question: Which forests are within baronies in the Republic of Ireland?
489.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?for  WHERE {     ?for a y2geoo:OSM_forest .   ?for geo:hasGeometry ?o .     ?o geo:asWKT ?forestGeo .      ?barony a y2geoo:OSI_Barony .     ?barony geo:hasGeometry ?o2 .     ?o2 geo:asWKT ?baronyGeo .  yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?ir.     ?ir geo:asWKT ?irWKT.    FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?forestGeo , ?baronyGeo ) && geof:sfWithin(?baronyGeo, ?irWKT )) }
